{"tid":1411812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（人手置頂）唔好忽略！請於網上聲援黃色媒體！","createTime":"2019-08-05T04:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:44:40.000Z","uid":119321,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"16dd94693b55055fcdf173cf64e5b8a666d73dd1","tid":1411812,"uid":119321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反擊五毛！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n想講特別係今朝之後，facebook同instagram一直有大量五毛藍絲擁入各媒體社交平台留言發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除咗蘋果立場等媒體，連港生活新假期個啲報導有關罷工都無一倖免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以自發係下面留言<br />\n[<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人加油</span></strong></span><br />\n[<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">支持大罷工</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n其他留言都可以！唔可以比簡體五毛入侵香港媒體，係我地幫返班記者嘅時候！求下大家一定要做！"},{"pid":"c1aa146047682803fab1ac1b671d2f4f54cc1677","tid":1411812,"uid":119321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eddfe04f4bc433c923629fdb969816c1200b1bab","tid":1411812,"uid":119321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:38:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"589c1edadfa36f301aa4ea9b359e576421ed8534","tid":1411812,"uid":119321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:40:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7b68edc6a25d414ca2eee4997f9d37118144dc96","tid":1411812,"uid":22104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:40:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">不要說：特首林鄭</span><br />\n試著說：嗰件垃圾<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">不要說：次次聽到林鄭開記者會都好嬲</span><br />\n試著說：嗰件垃圾並唔係我地香港人嘅特首<br />\n<br />\n當別人說：你個特首好垃圾<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">不要說：夠係你個特首</span><br />\n試著說：嗰件垃圾並唔係我地香港人選出黎嘅，所以佢並唔係我地特首<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不要只在心裡想佢辭職<br />\n我地要喺言語上行為上罷免佢<br />\n我地香港人已經罷免咗佢<br />\n<ins>不分藍色黃色撐反送中撐警</ins><br />\n所有香港人都覺得佢係垃圾，佢就係一件垃圾<br />\n我地香港人罷免佢</strong>"},{"pid":"8fb7ce21d5b8ba8cb1950ab7efddbbde86096b02","tid":1411812,"uid":119321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:40:59.000Z","msg":"推！聲援記者！"},{"pid":"3b43bb8d9119eef7a2c5efaf9ea9d50cfbe7d514","tid":1411812,"uid":271056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:41:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f604f33ba58b84ee862a4530a5cf839260f9381b","tid":1411812,"uid":119321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:43:02.000Z","msg":"幫手去各大媒體留言 只係阻大家2 3秒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a5f07fc1d167d2336801c531b57ba165e0821a","tid":1411812,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:44:05.000Z","msg":"支那狗不嬲好支持蘋果<br />\n得閒又可以上去撚三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb4a2d50f85a16da82c100eb819ce99ee4c03c5","tid":1411812,"uid":119321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:44:40.000Z","msg":"人生置頂！"}]}